    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Works that facilitate human activity and to provide for physical needs of people in or around a building generally by offering comfort, convenience, or protection. An example of usage is in distinguishing the architecture of a building from the furnishings that are placed in and around it.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
